(more cannon fire) (planes' engines)

46
00:07:21,496 --> 00:07:31,716
♫ "National Anthem plays" ♫

47
00:07:31,839 --> 00:07:34,059
narrator: Yes, this really happened.

48
00:07:36,676 --> 00:07:52,666
♪ (women singing the National Anthem) ♪

49
00:07:53,066 --> 00:09:22,506
(gun fire, cannon fire, bombing)

50
