Meantime, our warships stopped the Jap fleet.

51
00:09:36,883 --> 00:09:56,083
(loud plane's engine)

52
00:10:05,310 --> 00:10:07,440
Then suddenly, the trap is sprung.

53
00:10:10,642 --> 00:10:15,232
(plane takes off)

54
00:10:22,169 --> 00:10:24,109
Navy planes roared from the decks of our carriers.

55
00:10:24,831 --> 00:10:27,821
Army bombers, Marines...under destruction over a 300-mile

56
00:10:28,330 --> 00:10:29,250
battle area.

57
00:10:30,613 --> 00:10:39,163
(Cannons going off) (soaring gliders) (machine guns)

58
