67
00:12:41,993 --> 00:12:43,743
(bird "speaking"): I see just as free as they ever were.

68
00:12:46,550 --> 00:12:49,540
♪ (Music) ♪ (Marines' Hymn)

69
00:13:15,170 --> 00:13:17,990
