70
00:13:19,063 --> 00:13:21,873
But a big job is still to be done. Day after day, our

71
00:13:22,315 --> 00:13:25,415
control plane searches for survivors. Every tiny coral

72
00:13:25,752 --> 00:13:29,342
reef. Every distant mile of sea. Search for men who

73
00:13:29,518 --> 00:13:32,248
fought to the last round of ammunition and flew to

74
00:13:32,742 --> 00:13:34,912
the last drop of gas, and then crashed into the sea.

75
00:13:38,751 --> 00:13:43,451
Eight days. Nine days. Ten days without food or

76
00:13:43,699 --> 00:13:44,549
water.

77
