79
00:14:08,677 --> 00:14:10,347
Logan Ramsey...

80
00:14:20,375 --> 00:14:22,785
Frank Fessler. That's thirteen for Frank.

81
00:14:53,714 --> 00:14:56,654
(Female): Get those boys to the hospital. Please do,

82
00:14:57,270 --> 00:15:00,450
quickly. Get them to clean cots and cool sheets.

83
00:15:02,354 --> 00:15:05,794
Get them doctors and medicine, a nurse's soft hands.

84
00:15:06,938 --> 00:15:09,918
Get them to the hospital...hurry! Please!

85
00:15:11,362 --> 00:15:15,672
