86
00:15:16,980 --> 00:15:20,330
And on its roof, the red cross plainly marked, the

87
00:15:20,548 --> 00:15:23,868
symbol of mercy the enemy was bound to respect.

88
00:15:28,124 --> 00:15:29,244
(church bell peals (rings))

89
